PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 70 - which (a) declares that the flooding in July 2004 that affected the City of Peterborough and surrounding areas in the Province of ONTARIO, to be of concern to the federal government; and (b) authorizes the provision of financial assistance in that regard.
